{"word":"ὅτε","slug":"ὅτε","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὅτε</el></b> [<el>ὅ, τε</el>] temporal marker linking an event <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> another event, <b>when<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of coincidence in time <b><a href='B:470 7:28'>Mt 7:28</a>; <a href='B:480 1:32'>Mk 1:32</a>; <a href='B:490 2:21'>Lk 2:21</a>, <a href='B:490 2:42'>42</a>; <a href='B:510 12:6'>Ac 12:6</a>; <a href='B:530 13:11'>1 Cor 13:11b</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on eventuality <b><a href='B:490 17:22'>Lk 17:22</a>; <a href='B:500 4:21'>J 4:21</a>; <a href='B:500 9:4'>9:4</a>; R <a href='B:500 2:16'>2:16</a>; <a href='B:620 4:3'>2 Ti 4:3</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of coextensiveness in time, <b>when</b> = <b>as long as, while <a href='B:500 21:18'>J 21:18</a>; <a href='B:520 7:5'>Ro 7:5</a>; <a href='B:530 13:11'>1 Cor 13:11a</a>; <a href='B:650 9:17'>Hb 9:17</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὅταν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὅτι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}